'''Noehonese''' was the native language of the [[Noehon]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Noe'ha'on/Legends|Noe'ha'on]], that incorporated scent, mandibular clicks and shrills. Noehonese had no written form.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

Noehons had problems speaking any language but their own. However, they usually had to deal with offworlders, so learning [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] was usually needed. They, however, had more problems when dealing with written Basic.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

